metadata.title: 🧡🍯 The Honey 🐝🤍 | RTX 3070 | Ryzen 7 3700X | 32GB DDR4 | 1TB SSD

details.description:
*The Honey* Mid-Range Gaming PC is perfect for games, productivity, content creation, streaming, and more!

This PC is:
- ✅ **Thoroughly stress-tested and benchmarked** to ensure there are no stability issues and that the PC is performing as expected.

- 🎮 Perfect for playing any game at 1080p, 1440p, and even 4K - some benchmarks are listed below, and you can search "RTX 3070 + Ryzen 7 3700X benchmarks" on YouTube to find even more!  

Other:
- 💬 **If you have any questions or concerns, don't hesitate to reach out before buying!**
- 🌈 RGB: This PC uses **OpenRGB** for the graphics card and motherboard (case fans and cooler). OpenRGB comes preinstalled on the system and will be automatically added to your desktop upon account creation. ***NOTE:*** *If OpenRGB asks you to "resize the zones" upon first startup, **set each zone to "16"**.*
- 💾 Drivers: All drivers for **core system hardware** are preinstalled, but if you have any additional peripherals that you plan on using that require any software or drivers, **you'll have to install that yourself**.

Games and Benchmarks:  
*All benchmarks and games were run at 1080p resolution. More details in the individual results below.*
- Unigine Superposition (Extreme) - 8484 pts

- 3DMark Time Spy - 12721 pts
- BeamNG (Normal, Vulkan) - 180 FPS (EC USA), 125 FPS (WC USA)
- CS2 (Low) - 210 FPS
- The Finals (Medium) - 140 FPS

PC Specs:
- CPU: Ryzen 7 3700X
- Cooler: Thermalright Aqua Elite 240
- RAM: 32GB Timetec Pinnacle Konduit DDR4-3200 (2x16GB)
- Motherboard: JGINYUE B450 White ARGB
- Storage: Kingston NV2 1TB
- GPU: EVGA RTX 3070 XC3 Gaming 8GB
- Case: Sama ARGB-Q5 (White)
- PSU: Raidmax Cobra RX650AED
- OS: Windows 11 Pro
- Networking: Ethernet only (You can order a USB Wi-Fi adapter for under $15 on Amazon)

What’s in the Box?
- Gaming PC
- Power Cable
- Personalized Quick Start Guide  
   
**This is not a full setup, don’t expect a keyboard, mouse, or monitor.**
